03:13.819 --> 03:15.061
Yeah, but I'll just mention this.

03:15.181 --> 03:17.324
I was the only biologist.

03:18.866 --> 03:22.011
The other, there were probably 15

03:23.864 --> 03:25.246
outstanding economist.

03:26.648 --> 03:27.369
No historians?

03:28.551 --> 03:31.255
No.

